<title><anchor id="gnome-canvas-update-now">gnome_canvas_update_now ()</title>
<programlisting>void        gnome_canvas_update_now         (<link linkend="GnomeCanvas">GnomeCanvas</link> *canvas);</programlisting>
<para>
